#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Draco's Pig Mod"
msgstr "德拉科的豬模組"

#. ~ Description for Draco's Pig Mod
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Allows pigs to be tamed with cattle fodder."
msgstr "允許使用牛飼料馴養豬。"

#: .\pig_monsters.json
msgid "piglet"
msgid_plural "piglets"
msgstr[0] "小豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'piglet'}
#: .\pig_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A skittish piglet that snorts and roots randomly about the ground.  Much "
"easier to domesticate than feral adults."
msgstr "一隻易受驚的小豬，會隨機發出呼嚕聲並在地上拱土。比野生成年豬更容易馴養。"

#: .\pig_monsters.json
msgid "pig"
msgid_plural "pigs"
msgstr[0] "豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pig'}
#: .\pig_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A domesticated omnivore descended from the wild boar, intelligent and "
"inquisitive.  Left to its own devices, it can easily go feral but can be re-"
"tamed with sufficient time and trainer ability."
msgstr "一種由野豬馴化而來的雜食動物，聰明且好奇心強。若放任不管，很容易恢復野性，但可通過足夠時間和馴養者能力重新馴服。"
